---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact Kailash 2026 — Get in Touch for Your Pilgrimage | Kailash 2026" description="Contact the Kailash 2026 team for pilgrimage inquiries, permit assistance, travel planning, and cultural information. Reach us at kailash2026Lucas@outlook.com. We respond within 24-48 hours.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/kailash-golden.webp')] bg-cover bg-center"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-kailash-dark/70 via-kailash-dark/50 to-kailash-dark"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-kailash-gold text-sm md:text-base tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 font-light">
        We Are Here to Help
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Contact
        <span class="block text-kailash-gold mt-2">Us</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/80 mb-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
        Have questions about the Kailash pilgrimage? Ready to begin planning your journey? We would love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/60 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Reach out anytime — your sacred journey starts with a conversation.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12 text-sm text-white/50">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1">✉️ Fast Response</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1">🌏 Global Support</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1">🙏 All Faiths Welcome</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Card Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Email Contact Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-md text-center mb-12">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-kailash-gold/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-kailash-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4">Email Us</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Send us your questions, inquiries, or pilgrimage requests at any time. We read every message personally and respond with care and attention.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:kailash2026Lucas@outlook.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-kailash-gold text-kailash-dark px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-kailash-accent transition shadow-md">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          kailash2026Lucas@outlook.com
        </a>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-4">
          Click the email address above to open your email client and start writing to us directly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Response Time Card -->
      <div class="bg-kailash-dark rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-md text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What to Expect When You Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-4xl mb-3">⏱️</p>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-gold text-lg mb-2">Response Time</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">We respond to all inquiries within <span class="text-white font-semibold">24 to 48 hours</span>. Most messages receive a reply within one business day. During peak pilgrimage season (May-October) and around major festivals, response times may occasionally extend to 72 hours — we appreciate your patience.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-4xl mb-3">📝</p>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-gold text-lg mb-2">What We Need From You</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">To help us serve you better, please include in your email: your <span class="text-white font-semibold">full name</span>, your <span class="text-white font-semibold">country of residence</span>, the <span class="text-white font-semibold">approximate number of travelers</span> in your group, your <span class="text-white font-semibold">preferred travel dates</span> (or a range), and a <span class="text-white font-semibold">brief description</span> of what you are looking for. This helps us provide a relevant and personalized response.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-4xl mb-3">🌐</p>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-kailash-gold text-lg mb-2">Languages We Support</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">You can write to us in <span class="text-white font-semibold">English</span>, <span class="text-white font-semibold">Hindi</span>, <span class="text-white font-semibold">Chinese (Mandarin)</span>, or <span class="text-white font-semibold">Japanese</span>. We will respond in the same language whenever possible. For other languages, we will do our best to accommodate or use English as a common medium of communication.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What to Contact Us About -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-kailash-gold text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-3 font-medium">How We Can Help</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4">What to Contact Us About</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Whatever you need, we are here. Here are the most common reasons pilgrims reach out to us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🗺️</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">Pilgrimage Planning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Not sure which route, dates, or itinerary suits you? Tell us about your interests, fitness level, and available time, and we will recommend the best options for your sacred journey.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📋</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">Permit & Visa Questions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Confused about the Tibet Travel Permit, Chinese visa requirements, or border entry procedures? We can explain the entire process clearly and help you navigate every requirement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💰</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">Travel Planning & Guidance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Request a detailed quote tailored to your group size, preferred dates, and service level. We provide transparent pricing with no hidden fees — what we quote is what you pay.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏔️</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">Physical Preparation Advice</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Wondering if you are fit enough for the kora? Ask us about training recommendations, altitude acclimatization strategies, and what to expect physically at each stage of the journey.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🙏</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">Cultural & Religious Guidance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Want to understand the rituals, arrange a special puja, or learn about the customs specific to your tradition? Our cultural experts are happy to provide detailed information and arrange ceremonies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">Safety & Medical Concerns</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Have a pre-existing medical condition or safety concern? Contact us for a candid discussion about whether the kora is right for you and what accommodations we can provide to support your journey.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Info -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-md">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-6">A Note From Our Founder</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p>
            "When I first set out to create Kailash 2026, I wanted to build more than a travel service. I wanted to create a genuine connection point between the world's pilgrims and the mountain that had transformed my own life. Every email we receive represents someone's sacred intention — a hope, a prayer, a dream of standing before Kailash.
          </p>
          <p>
            I read every message personally. Whether you are a Hindu devotee from Varanasi planning your first pilgrimage, a Buddhist practitioner from Tokyo seeking to walk in Milarepa's footsteps, a Bön pilgrim honoring your ancestral traditions, or a Jain seeker drawn to the mountain of Rishabhanatha's nirvana — you are welcome here.
          </p>
          <p>
            The journey to Kailash is not easy. The altitude is extreme, the terrain is demanding, and the permit process can feel overwhelming. But I promise you this: when you stand before that pyramid-shaped peak at sunrise, when you cross Drolma La pass at 5,630 meters and hang your prayer flags in the wind, every challenge along the way will reveal itself as part of the blessing.
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark">
            Reach out. Let us begin this journey together."
          </p>
          <p class="text-kailash-gold font-medium">— Lucas, Founder of Kailash 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Contact Reminder -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-kailash-dark">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Begin Your Sacred Journey?</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-lg mb-8">
        The 2026 Horse Year is approaching. We encourage you to reach out early to plan your pilgrimage and prepare for this once-in-a-lifetime journey.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:kailash2026Lucas@outlook.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-kailash-gold text-kailash-dark px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl hover:bg-kailash-accent transition shadow-lg">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
        </svg>
        Email Us Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
